Top level classes for pseudospectral code:

System {
   Mixture
   UnitCell
   SpaceGroup
   Grid
   Basis
}

Supporting classes and functions:

class Vector<int D> -> templated version of existing Vector class
class IntVector<int D> -> templated version of existing IntVector class

class GridField<int D> - representation of field on an fft grid

Functions to convert basis to grid and grid to basis.

